useCase.name: Monitoring of children
useCase.porpuse: Detect at the moment when the child is distracted while performing academic tasks.
useCase.porpuse_i: Detect at the moment when the child is distracted while performing academic tasks.
useCase.pre_condition: Authenticated users, both student and tutor.
useCase.pre_condition_i: Authenticated users, both student and tutor.
useCase.precondition_i: Authenticated users, both student and tutor.

useCase.name: Configure objects for permitted use
useCase.porpuse: Specify which objects the student can use while performing school tasks. Any other objects will be considered as distractors.
useCase.porpuse_i: Specify which objects the student can use while performing school tasks. Any other objects will be considered as distractors.
useCase.description_interpret: The tutor registers each of the objects that the child can use while performing school tasks. The model learns from each of the selected objects.
useCase.description_original: The tutor registers each of the objects that the child can use while performing school tasks. The model learns from each of the selected objects.

_name._text: Secuence Diagram - Configure objects for permitted use

useCase.name: Issuing alerts to the parents
useCase.description_interpret: When the device identifies the student''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''s distraction, the system generates a notification and stores it to be shared with the rest of the system components.
useCase.description_original: When the device identifies the student''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''s distraction, the system generates a notification and stores it to be shared with the rest of the system components.

_name._text: Secuence Diagram - Issuing alerts to the parents

useCase.name: Persuade the student
useCase.porpuse: Ensure that the student stops being distracted and continues with their tasks.
useCase.porpuse_i: Ensure that the student stops being distracted and continues with their tasks.
useCase.description_interpret: Once the system has saved the identification of the distraction or event, it generates a notification to be played by the device, prompting the student to stop the distraction and continue with their tasks.
useCase.description_original: Once the system has saved the identification of the distraction or event, it generates a notification to be played by the device, prompting the student to stop the distraction and continue with their tasks.

useCase.name: View Report
useCase.description_interpret: The tutor can view real-time data of the events that have occurred.
useCase.description_original: The tutor can view real-time data of the events that have occurred.

useCase.name: View Historial
useCase.porpuse: Display the historical report data requested by the tutor.
useCase.porpuse_i: Display the historical report data requested by the tutor.
useCase.description_interpret: The tutor selects the parameters they wish to display in the report.
useCase.description_original: The tutor selects the parameters they wish to display in the report.

useCase.name: Login
useCase.porpuse: Authenticate in the system to access the application''''s functionalities.
useCase.porpuse_i: Authenticate in the system to access the application''''s functionalities.
useCase.pre_condition: No user authenticated in the application.
useCase.pre_condition_i: No user authenticated in the application.
useCase.description_interpret: The application user enters the credentials with which they are registered as a system user.
useCase.description_original: The application user enters the credentials with which they are registered as a system user.

useCase.name: Reset Password
useCase.porpuse: When the user has forgotten their password, or wishes to change their password.
useCase.porpuse_i: When the user has forgotten their password, or wishes to change their password.
useCase.pre_condition: No user authenticated in the application.
useCase.pre_condition_i: No user authenticated in the application.
useCase.description_interpret: The user enters the identifying information along with the new password twice to confirm it has been entered correctly.
useCase.description_original: The user enters the identifying information along with the new password twice to confirm it has been entered correctly.
useCase.precondition_i: No user authenticated in the application.

useCase.name: Sign up
useCase.pre_condition: No user authenticated in the application.
useCase.pre_condition_i: No user authenticated in the application.
useCase.post_condition: User registered in the Torddis system.
useCase.post_condition_i: User registered in the Torddis system.
useCase.description_interpret: The person wishing to register must enter all the required information requested by the system.
useCase.description_original: The person wishing to register must enter all the required information requested by the system.

useCase.name: Register Device
useCase.porpuse: Associate the device with the student.
useCase.porpuse_i: Associate the device with the student.
useCase.description_interpret: The tutor registers the device via the MAC address in the mobile application, which also involves training the model with the student''''s face to be monitored.
useCase.description_original: The tutor registers the device via the MAC address in the mobile application, which also involves training the model with the student''''s face to be monitored.

useCase.name: Train the model with the student''s face
useCase.name_i: Train the model with the student''s face
useCase.porpuse: For the system to recognise the child to be monitored.
useCase.porpuse_i: For the system to recognise the child to be monitored.
useCase.description_interpret: The tutor requests the student to be present in front of the camera so that the system can take the necessary photographs for recognition.
useCase.description_original: The tutor requests the student to be present in front of the camera so that the system can take the necessary photographs for recognition.

_name._text: Secuence Diagram - Train the model with the student''s face

useCase.name: Register Student
useCase.post_condition: Student registered in the Torddis system.
useCase.post_condition_i: Student registered in the Torddis system.
useCase.description_interpret: The tutor enters all the student''s information requested by the system.
useCase.description_original: The tutor enters all the student''s information requested by the system.
